  "intro": "<p>\n</p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, bl<x>inkMacSystemFont, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px;\">创作手记：</span></p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, bl<x>inkMacSystemFont, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px;\">用一首歌，让更多人知道、了解、爱上一个地方，是个美好的企图。</span></p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, bl<x>inkMacSystemFont, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px;\">再过500年，我们不在了，光崀还在，《光之崀》还在。所以，木心说：岁月不饶人，我也未曾饶过岁月——只有人文能够永恒。</span></p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, bl<x>inkMacSystemFont, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px;\">《光之崀》唱的是光崀的自然风水、文心氤氲、艺术探梦和继往开来，有天光开合、云淡风轻、也有悲欣交集。光崀会像北京的宋庄、浙江的乌镇，成为艺术家安身立命、开天辟地的家园，成为易经“西南得朋”的艺术道场。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 32px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">《光之崀》</span>的词、曲、唱，整合了这些价值元素，给人带来雪山金辉的光崀气象与辉煌。</span></p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, bl<x>inkMacSystemFont, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 14px;\">希望这首歌能够为光崀汇聚更多的人气和能量，使更多的艺术家相濡以沫、同频共情、惺惺相惜<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 2em;\">。</span></span></p>\n <p></p>",
